These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, hiking, drawing, skydiving
There are 4 different favourite colors: green, coral, amber, mauve
4 different games are played: scrabble, mah-jongg, canasta, poker
4 different pets are kept: cat, dog, goat, goldfish
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, helicopter, taxi, tram
 1. the person driving the car is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
 2. the person playing poker is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person driving the tram##2
 3. the owner of the cat is the person driving the tram##1
 4. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 5. the person driving the car is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person playing canasta##2
 6. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 7. the person driving the helicopter is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 8. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
 9. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
10. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |         3          |     4     |
| Hobby           | drawing | puzzles   | skydiving | hiking |
| Color   | green      | coral | amber              | mauve |
| Game   | scrabble       | mah-jongg     | poker               | canasta    |
| Pet           | dog        | goat     | goldfish           | cat       |
| Transport     | helicopter | taxi     | car                | tram      |

