.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, july, april, november
City: london, san-francisco, berlin, hannover
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, punk, r&b, techno
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, subway, helicopter, car
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, sailing, tennis, volleyball
 1. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 2. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 3. the person traveling to san-francisco is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person driving the subway##2
 4. the fan of techno is the person who's sport is handball##1
 5. the person driving the helicopter is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 6. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
 7. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 8. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
 9. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
10. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person driving the car##1
11. the person who's sport is handball is the person who's birthday is in april##1
12. the person who's birthday is in may is the person traveling to berlin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |     2      |       3        |      4      |
| Birthday          | april       | july      | may      | november      |
| City           | hannover | san-francisco | berlin | london |
| Music-Genre   | techno          | punk       | r&b            | gospel      |
| Transport           | airplane            | helicopter    | subway           | car       |
| Sport         | handball        | sailing    | tennis         | volleyball  |

