City: nizza, hamburg, colone, venice
4 different games are played: snooker, go, backgammon, canasta
 1. the british is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 2. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 3. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the japanese##1
 4. the person traveling to nizza is the person playing go##1
 5. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
 6. the person eating asparagus is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the person playing snooker##2
 7. the british is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
 8. the person eating grapefruit is the person playing backgammon##1
 9. the british is the person traveling to venice##1
10. the colombian is on the far left##1
11. the colombian is the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Food          | banana    | asparagus  | strawberry | grapefruit |
| Hobby   | puzzles   | writing        | gardening | video-games     |
| Nationality   | colombian | british    | pakistani  | japanese   |
| City           | colone     | venice      | nizza | hamburg        |
| Game         | snooker      | canasta | go      | backgammon     |

