.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, lemonade, tea
There 4 different types of food: avocado, corn, pomegranate, spinach
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, marigold, lily, daisy
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, september, december, january
4 different pets are kept: cat, rabbit, rat, pony
 1. the owner of the rat is the person eating avocado##1
 2. the owner of the rabbit is between the person who growsdaffodil and the person who growsmarigold##2
 3. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 4. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 5. the person who growsmarigold is between the person who's birthday is in february and the owner of the cat##2
 6. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who growslily##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is the owner of the pony##1
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is between the owner of the rabbit and the person who growslily##2
10. the person eating spinach is on the far left##1
11. the person eating corn is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |      4       |
| Beverage      | tea     | almond-milk | lemonade    | 7up          |
| Food          | spinach | avocado     | pomegranate | corn         |
| Flower   | lily    | marigold       | daisy         | daffodil        |
| Birthday         | january  | september     | february     | december |
| Pet     | cat     | rat      | rabbit   | pony          |

