 6. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 7. the person who's hobby is writing is between the person watching sports movies and the person who likes white##2
 8. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 9. the owner of the rat is the person who's sport is rugby##1
10. the owner of the rat is between the owner of the dog and the owner of the turtle##2
11. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far right##1
12. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1

