 5. the person playing backgammon is the person watching adventure movies##1
 6. the person who likes apricot is the person drinking coffee##1
 7. the person driving the taxi is the person drinking lemonade##1
 8. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 9. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
10. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person playing poker##1
11. the person playing poker is between the person watching adventure movies and the person driving the taxi##2
12. the person playing domino is between the person driving the roller and the person drinking coffee##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2        |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea      | coffee         | lemonade | juice      |
| Movie-Genre           | adventure | fantasy | crime | satire     |
| Color   | lilac         | apricot          | chestnut  | green |
| Game         | backgammon        | poker  | domino | scrabble   |
| Transport     | skateboard    | subway         | taxi     | roller     |

