 6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
 7. the person eating blueberry is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 8. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who growslily##1
 9. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person who growslily##1
