 2. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 3. the person drinking juice is between the fan of trance and the person who's birthday is in april##2
 4. the person who's birthday is in april is the fan of d&b##1
 5. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking juice and the person who likes light-blue##2
