4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, tiparillo, aristoff, pall-mall
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, western, disaster, documentary
 1. the fan of salsa is the malaysian##1
 2. the person watching documentary movies is between the thai and the old-henry-smoker##2
 3. the person watching western movies is between the tiparillo-smoker and the person watching disaster movies##2
 4. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
 5. the fan of gospel is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
 6. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
 7. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
 8. the fan of gospel is the aristoff-smoker##1
 9. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
10. the person traveling to hamburg is the japanese##1
11. the japanese is the pall-mall-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |      3      |      4       |
