| Music-Genre   | salsa      | dubstep   | gospel      | classical    |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | pakistani | thai        | japanese     |
| Cigar         | old-henry  | tiparillo  | aristoff     | pall-mall      |
| Movie-Genre     | animation | documentary      | western   | disaster       |

 